<p><strong>Stock turnover (in days)</strong> = The stock turnover (in days) saved. The stock turnover (in days) represents the number of days that you want your stock to last. The stock turnover (in days) is saved for each variation per warehouse in the <strong>Warehouse</strong> tab of the variation.</p>
</li>
