</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings as desired. Pay attention to the information given in table <a href="#table-event-procedure-generate-reorder-document">Table 6</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Place a check mark next to the option <strong>Active</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
